metadata.name: Dinner on Piccolo
metadata.description: Extreme anime fan; Anime and Music have always inspired cyberpunk work, just as my favorite character who is Goku from Dragon Ball this piece contains elements of my favorite anime one piece and my favorite game cyberpunk wired in away to display my thoughts on Goku for the foodie and inspiration that he isâ€¦This is not my First nor will it be my last piece depicting the character Goku but it will be one of my BEST.
